@prefix ex: <https://vocab.cfaa.eus/broaching/> .
ex:JogPanel a ex:InterfazUsuario ;
    ex:textoExtracto """Turn the CNC off. Turn the CNC off. CNC OFF Jog keyboard for jogging the axes. Keys to select axes and jog them in the positive direction. Keys to select axes and jog them in the negative direction. Keys to select the axes and keys to select the jogging direction. Both keys (axis and direction) must be pressed to jog the axis. Rapid key. When pressing this key while moving an axis, the CNC applies the rapid feedrate. Feed selectors. jog 1 1 10 10 100 100 1000 10000 Sector for the type of jog; continuous / incremental jog or handwheels. • In handwheel mode, it selects the multiplying for the handwheel pulses (x1, x10 o x100). • In incremental mode, it selects the incremental value of the axis movements. 90100 80 70 110 60 120 50 130 40 140 30 150 20 160 10 170 4 180 2 190 0 200 FEED Selector of percentage of feedrate override, between 0% and 200%, for jog and automatic movements. Execution keys. Cycle start key (START). Execute the selected program in automatic mode, a block in MDI/MDA mode, etc. Cycle stop key (STOP). Interrupt the execution of the CNC. Reset key. RESET It initializes the system setting the initial conditions as defined by machine parameters. Single-block execution mode. SINGLE When selecting the "single block" execution mode, the program simulation will be interrupted at the end of each block. Home search. ZERO Spindle control. Start the spindle clockwise. Stop the spindle. Start the spindle counteclockwise. To vary the spindle speed percentually. _ Spindle orientation. Selector of percentage of 708090100110 spindle speed override 60 120 between 0% and 200%. 50 130 40 140 30 150 20 160 10 170 4 180 2 200190 0 SPEED""" .

ex:RapidKey a ex:ComponenteElectrico ;
    ex:textoExtracto """Rapid key. When pressing this key while moving an axis, the CNC applies the rapid feedrate.""" .

ex:FeedSelector a ex:ComponenteElectrico ;
    ex:textoExtracto """Feed selectors. jog 1 1 10 10 100 100 1000 10000 Sector for the type of jog; continuous / incremental jog or handwheels. • In handwheel mode, it selects the multiplying for the handwheel pulses (x1, x10 o x100). • In incremental mode, it selects the incremental value of the axis movements.""" .

ex:CycleStartKey a ex:ComponenteElectrico ;
    ex:textoExtracto """Cycle start key (START). Execute the selected program in automatic mode, a block in MDI/MDA mode, etc.""" .

ex:CycleStopKey a ex:ComponenteElectrico ;
    ex:textoExtracto """Cycle stop key (STOP). Interrupt the execution of the CNC.""" .

ex:ResetKey a ex:ComponenteElectrico ;
    ex:textoExtracto """Reset key. RESET It initializes the system setting the initial conditions as defined by machine parameters.""" .

ex:SingleBlockExecutionMode a ex:ModoOperacion ;
    ex:textoExtracto """Single-block execution mode. SINGLE When selecting the "single block" execution mode, the program simulation will be interrupted at the end of each block.""" .

ex:HomeSearchKey a ex:ComponenteElectrico ;
    ex:textoExtracto """Home search. ZERO""" .

ex:SpindleClockwiseStartKey a ex:ComponenteElectrico ;
    ex:textoExtracto """Spindle control. Start the spindle clockwise.""" .

ex:SpindleStopKey a ex:ComponenteElectrico ;
    ex:textoExtracto """Stop the spindle.""" .

ex:SpindleCounterclockwiseStartKey a ex:ComponenteElectrico ;
    ex:textoExtracto """Start the spindle counteclockwise.""" .

ex:SpindleSpeedOverrideSelector a ex:ComponenteElectrico ;
    ex:textoExtracto """To vary the spindle speed percentually. _ Spindle orientation. Selector of percentage of 708090100110 spindle speed override 60 120 between 0% and 200%.""" .